比利·乔尔 (Billy Joel) 宣布推出数十年来首支单曲《Turn The Lights Back On》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-joel-announces-first-single-in-decades-with-turn-the-lights-back-on-3575040?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billy-乔尔宣布数十年来第一张重新打开灯光的单曲Anagricel DuranMon, 22 Jan 2024 19:22:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3575040 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比利·乔尔的“Turn The Lights Back On”单曲艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该曲目定于 2 月 1 日发行</p><p>比利<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-joel-announces-first-single-in-decades-with-turn-the-lights-back-on-3575040">·乔尔 (Billy Joel) 宣布数十年来首张单曲《Turn The Lights Back On》的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比利·乔尔的“Turn The Lights Back On”单曲艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Billy-Joel-Turn-The-Lights-Back-On-single-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/aritsts/billy-joel">比利·乔尔 (Billy Joel)</a>宣布推出《Turn The Lights Back On》，这是他自 2007 年以来的第一首个人歌曲，也是自 1993 年以来的第二首个人歌曲。</p><p> 《Turn The Lights Back On》将于 2 月 1 日通过哥伦比亚发行。它将在所有流媒体平台上发售，并推出限量版 7 英寸黑胶唱片。您可以在此处预先保存/预订。</p><p>这首歌还将在他的官方 YouTube 频道上附上歌词视频。乔尔与格莱美提名歌曲作者兼制作人弗雷迪·韦克斯勒（同时也是这首歌的制作人）、亚瑟·培根和韦恩·赫克托（<a href="/artists/nicki-minaj">妮琪·米娜</a>、 <a href="/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a> ）一起创作了这首歌曲。</p><p>乔尔开始 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-joel-teases-his-first-new-music-in-17-years-3574740">调侃新音乐，这将是他 17 年来的第一首新素材</a>，上个月，这位歌手推出了官方 TikTok 账户，分享他在舞台上谈论新音乐的片段。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2aOPczuKVt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 4